        		<p>I thought i remembered that the light suits in the original film were decorated with reflective strips and then lit using a variant on the old front-projection special effects system  (<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Front_projection" rel="nofollow">http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Front_projection</a>), rather as Lucas originally tried to do with the light sabers in &#8220;Star Wars&#8221;.</p>
    		</div>
			<div class="comment-reply-link"><a class='comment-reply-link' href='/tron-legacy-light-suit-costume/15850/?replytocom=15885#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm("comment-15885", "15885", "respond", "15850")'>Reply</a></div>			<ul class='children'>
